Keh do ki tum.Kal dil dukhaya tha meine tumhara,
Is baat ka aaj tak mujhko hai gham,
yeh sochkar maaf kar dena mujhko,
meri yeh pehli mohabbat hai janam,mohabbat hai janam,Yehi aada tho ek sitam hai
Suno tumhe meri kasam hai
Keh do ki tum.Shikwe gile,shikwe gile,
Shikwe gile saab hai kal ki kahani,
Ab jindagi bhar khafa hum na honge,
Ab mein tumhara hoon aaur bas tumhara
Maar jaao bhi tho juda hum na honge
Ab khafa hum na honge
